* {{ill|Genroku|ja|Genroku|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1688|ja|1688th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – The era name changes from {{ill|Jōkyō (Japan)|ja|貞享|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} to Genroku.
